data.description: This meticulously remodeled ranch-style home presents an irresistible blend of timeless charm and contemporary elegance. Boasting 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a host of modern upgrades, this is the epitome of comfortable living. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed interior featuring an open-concept layout seamlessly connecting the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Every room has been ungraded with modern fixtures, new flooring and fresh paint throughout. The exterior has a new roof, siding and windows as well as a newly encapsulated crawl space, all within the last few years, and all warranties transfer. Don't miss the opportunity to make this impeccably remodeled home yours.
